== 实例 ==
扩展适应包括[[羽毛|羽毛]]的共同选择，羽毛最初是为用于保温的和用于展示的功能而演化的，后来被用于鸟类的飞行。另一个例子则是早期鱼类的[[肺|肺]]，它们后来演化为陆生[[脊椎动物|脊椎动物]]的肺，但同时还通过扩展适应成为了一些鱼类体内用来调节浮力的器官——[[鳔|鳔]]。<ref>{{cite journal |author = Colleen Farmer |year = 1997 |title = Did Lungs and the Intracardiac Shunt Evolve to Oxygenate the Heart in Vertebrates? |url = https://archive.org/details/sim_paleobiology_summer-1997_23_3/page/358 |journal = Paleobiology |volume = 23 |pages = 358–372 |publisher = [[Paleontological_Society|Paleontological Society]] |jstor = 2401109|issue = 3 |ref = harv}}</ref>

